    div(class="template-section m-a")
        section(class="template-content")
            
            div(class="row-flex s-actividad u-animationFadeDown")
                div(class="row")
                    h5 Decide when the speakers agree, when they disagree or when they give a neutral opinion.
                    div(class="col-center col xs12 md7")
                        div(class="c-cardGreen")
                            div(class="c-cardGreenContent")
                                p Marco was driving his car on the Caracas Avenue in Bogotá. At the corner of Caracas and 19th, he crashed against a red car. A person in the red car has a minor wound.
                div(class="col xs12 md6")
                    div(class="row mb50") 
                        p #[strong: span(class="u-textColor_4-dark") 1.] #[strong: span(class="u-textColor_2") A]: I don’t think we need to go to the hospital.  
                        p #[strong: span(class="u-textColor_5 ml20") B]: In my very personal view, I think we should call the doctor.
                        div(class="row-flex")
                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="SelectRadio_1" name="selection_1" value="1")
                            label(for="SelectRadio_1" class="c-CheckSelected col-flex ml10 mr10" ng-click="txtcaptura_e='in'") Agree
                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="SelectRadio_2" name="selection_1" value="2")
                            label(for="SelectRadio_2" class="c-CheckSelected col-flex ml10 mr10" ng-click="txtcaptura_e='to'") Disagree
                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="SelectRadio_3" name="selection_1" value="3")
                            label(for="SelectRadio_3" class="c-CheckSelected col-flex ml10 mr10" ng-click="txtcaptura_e='on'") Neutral position

                        div(class="row mb50") 
                        p #[strong: span(class="u-textColor_4-dark") 2.] #[strong: span(class="u-textColor_2") A]: Calling the police is the only thing I can think of.  
                        p #[strong: span(class="u-textColor_5 ml20") B]: I tend to think that we are making the right decision.
                        div(class="row-flex")
                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="SelectRadio_4" name="selection_2" value="1")
                            label(for="SelectRadio_4" class="c-CheckSelected col-flex ml10 mr10" ng-click="txtcaptura_e='in'") Agree
                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="SelectRadio_5" name="selection_2" value="2")
                            label(for="SelectRadio_5" class="c-CheckSelected col-flex ml10 mr10" ng-click="txtcaptura_e='to'") Disagree
                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="SelectRadio_6" name="selection_2" value="3")
                            label(for="SelectRadio_6" class="c-CheckSelected col-flex ml10 mr10" ng-click="txtcaptura_e='on'") Neutral position

                        div(class="row mb50") 
                        p #[strong: span(class="u-textColor_4-dark") 3.] #[strong: span(class="u-textColor_2") A]: How about just taking the car to the garage and have it fixed there? 
                        p #[strong: span(class="u-textColor_5 ml20") B]:  I honestly feel that this is not going to work.
                        div(class="row-flex")
                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="SelectRadio_7" name="selection_3" value="1")
                            label(for="SelectRadio_7" class="c-CheckSelected col-flex ml10 mr10" ng-click="txtcaptura_e='in'") Agree
                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="SelectRadio_8" name="selection_3" value="2")
                            label(for="SelectRadio_8" class="c-CheckSelected col-flex ml10 mr10" ng-click="txtcaptura_e='to'") Disagree
                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="SelectRadio_9" name="selection_3" value="3")
                            label(for="SelectRadio_9" class="c-CheckSelected col-flex ml10 mr10" ng-click="txtcaptura_e='on'") Neutral position

                div(class="col xs12 md6")
                    div(class="row mb50") 
                        p #[strong: span(class="u-textColor_4-dark") 4.] #[strong: span(class="u-textColor_2") A]: Fixing the car should be around US500! 
                        p #[strong: span(class="u-textColor_5 ml20") B]:  As I see it, we need to bring in an expert.
                        div(class="row-flex")
                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="SelectRadio_10" name="selection_4" value="1")
                            label(for="SelectRadio_10" class="c-CheckSelected col-flex ml10 mr10" ng-click="txtcaptura_e='in'") Agree
                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="SelectRadio_11" name="selection_4" value="2")
                            label(for="SelectRadio_11" class="c-CheckSelected col-flex ml10 mr10" ng-click="txtcaptura_e='to'") Disagree
                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="SelectRadio_12" name="selection_4" value="3")
                            label(for="SelectRadio_12" class="c-CheckSelected col-flex ml10 mr10" ng-click="txtcaptura_e='on'") Neutral position

                        div(class="row mb50") 
                        p #[strong: span(class="u-textColor_4-dark") 5.] #[strong: span(class="u-textColor_2") A]: The red car should have stopped! 
                        p #[strong: span(class="u-textColor_5 ml20") B]: My opinion is that the red car driver is right. The traffic light was red for you!
                        div(class="row-flex")
                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="SelectRadio_13" name="selection_5" value="1")
                            label(for="SelectRadio_13" class="c-CheckSelected col-flex ml10 mr10" ng-click="txtcaptura_e='in'") Agree
                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="SelectRadio_14" name="selection_5" value="2")
                            label(for="SelectRadio_14" class="c-CheckSelected col-flex ml10 mr10" ng-click="txtcaptura_e='to'") Disagree
                            input(class="c-inputRadio" type="radio" id="SelectRadio_15" name="selection_5" value="3")
                            label(for="SelectRadio_15" class="c-CheckSelected col-flex ml10 mr10" ng-click="txtcaptura_e='on'") Neutral position

    |
